# Figma MCP Implementation Rules

- Treat Figma MCP code output (often React + Tailwind) as design and behavior reference, not final project code style.
- Translate Figma output into this repo's stack and conventions (Vue 3 + Vuetify + existing project patterns).
- Reuse existing project tokens, components, and typography before creating new styling or duplicated UI primitives.
- Prefer existing routing, state, and data-fetch patterns when wiring behavior from Figma designs.
- Target 1:1 visual and interaction parity with Figma, while prioritizing project design-system tokens when conflicts occur.
